metadata.name: Eve
metadata.description:
"Serenity"


טוֹב וָרָע ("tov wa-raʿ")


We are one family. According to Abrahamic religions biting from the fruits of the tree of the knowledge of good and evil imbued humanity with evil. Forcing humanity to sift through this new mixture of good and evil to liberate the good within and extract the evil. 


Serenity is selfish but it can be shared. Luigi knows you'll liberate the good and extract the evil.

Make apple sauce. 🍎👏
